file.name: logAPI.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
    title: Log API
    version: v1
    description: Log API for Channel logs
servers:
    -
        url: echo.3scale.net
        
        description: Development Container Gateway URL on the Openshift
paths:
    /channels/technical/logs/v1/log:
        post:
            requestBody:
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            type: object
                            properties:
                                timeStamp:
                                    type: string
                                userAgent:
                                    type: string
                                deviceInfo:
                                    type: string
                                originURL:
                                    type: string
                                operationComponent:
                                    type: string
                                logMask:
                                    type: string
                                hostNodeIp:
                                    type: string
                                userName:
                                    type: string
                                auditDescription:
                                    type: string
                                auditDetail:
                                    type: string
                required: true
            parameters:
                -
                    name: channel
                    schema:
                        type: string
                    in: header
                    required: true
                -
                    name: ip
                    schema:
                        type: string
                    in: header
                    required: true
                -
                    name: dialect
                    schema:
                        type: string
                    in: header
                    required: true
                -
                    name: companyId
                    schema:
                        type: string
                    in: header
            responses:
                '200':
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                $ref: '#/components/schemas/result'
                    description: Return operation result.
            summary: Create a log record for Channel
            description: Create a log record for Channel log
components:
    schemas:
        result:
            properties:
                '500':
                    description: Internal Server Error
                returnCode:
                    type: integer
                reasonCode:
                    type: integer
                messageText:
                    type: string
                default:
                    description: Unexpected error
